<p>Damnit <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604893084" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5028224); return false;">Crashington</a></span>, you were supposed to let this one fester!</p>
<p>Anyways, first SCP article I ever wrote onto the mainsite, whose execution I <em>absolutely</em> butchered. Foundation send SCP Psychiatrists to deal with shitty relationships marked by a bored god.</p>
