<p>McB and I are planning on turning MWDOT into a canon/GOI, or at least a tag. Why? Fuck if I know.</p>
<p>I blame <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2969291&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1604893084" alt="XilasCrowe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2969291)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xilascrowe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2969291); return false;">XilasCrowe</a></span>. I always have, and I always will.</p>
